NOTE ON THIRD-PARTY ASSETS

The MIT license above covers ONLY the configuration files and scripts authored
in this repository. It does NOT cover the visual assets those scripts fetch and
install at runtime, which keep their own upstream licenses:

  * Chicago95 (icons, cursors, sounds, GTK theme) -- GPL-3.0
        https://github.com/grassmunk/Chicago95
  * Win2k icon theme (KDE-Store item 1120706)     -- see the item's page
  * ReactOS assets (optional)                      -- GPL-2.0 / mixed
        https://github.com/reactos/reactos

None of those asset bytes are redistributed here; the installers download them
from their upstreams so their licenses travel with them.
